*DESCRIPTION_START
Before you stands a dark-robed figure, surrounded by an eerie nimbus of pure,
chaotic energy. Two pinpoints of intense, flickering light shine out from
beneath its cowl, framed by long shimmering hair of no definable color. Wildly
shifting distortions ripple through the air as the creature passes, making it
impossible to determine its true race or even gender.
*DESCRIPTION_END
