*DESCRIPTION_START
You see what appears to be an animate shadow wreathed in colorless distortion,
like heat waves pouring off of its form. The outlines of this bizarre beast
constantly blur and change in subtle ways, almost as though it is having some
trouble maintaining its shape in this plane. It fights in eerie silence,
making no sound other than the scrape of its claws against the ground as it
leaps to the attack.
*DESCRIPTION_END
